<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gab's Scrapbook | Nursing & Notes</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Homemade+Apple&family=Special+Elite&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #e6dfcf;
            --ink: #2b2621;
            --sage-tape: rgba(135, 169, 130, 0.5);
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/papyrus.png');
            color: var(--ink);
            font-family: 'Special Elite', serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .scrapbook {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        header {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--ink);
        }

        header h1 { font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive; font-size: 5rem; margin: 0; }

        /* Artists - With Hover Effect */
        .artist-section {
            grid-column: 1 / -1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .polaroid {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 15px 15px 35px 15px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            width: 160px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .polaroid img { width: 100%; height: 160px; object-fit: cover; }
        
        .polaroid:nth-child(odd) { transform: rotate(-2deg); }
        .polaroid:nth-child(even) { transform: rotate(3deg); }

        .polaroid-caption {
            font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            margin-top: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Hover Detail Overlay */
        .polaroid-detail {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.95);
            padding: 20px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .polaroid:hover { transform: scale(1.1) rotate(0deg); z-index: 5; }
        .polaroid:hover .polaroid-detail { opacity: 1; }

        /* Paper Scraps */
        .paper-scrap {
            background: #fdfaf0;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative;
        }

        .tape {
            position: absolute;
            width: 80px;
            height: 30px;
            background: var(--sage-tape);
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%) rotate(-2deg);
        }

        /* About Me Section */
        .about-scrap { grid-column: 1 / 2; transform: rotate(-1deg); }
        
        /* Songs Section - No Hover */
        .songs-scrap { grid-column: 2 / 4; transform: rotate(1deg); }
        
        .song-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        iframe { border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .scrapbook { display: block; }
            .polaroid { width: 100%; margin-bottom: 20px; }
            .paper-scrap { margin-bottom: 40px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="scrapbook">
    <header>
        <h1>Gab</h1>
        <p>— A soul full of stories and dreams —</p>
    </header>

    <div class="artist-section">
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/Clairo.jpg" alt="Clairo">
            <div class="polaroid-caption">Clairo</div>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">The comfort of bedroom pop and soft melodies.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/CocteuTwins.jpg" alt="Cocteau Twins">
            <div class="polaroid-caption">Cocteau Twins</div>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">Ethereal, dream-like soundscapes.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/FleetwoodMac.jpg" alt="Fleetwood Mac">
            <div class="polaroid-caption">Fleetwood Mac</div>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">Timeless harmonies and classic storytelling.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/WeyesBlood.jpg" alt="Weyes Blood">
            <div class="polaroid-caption">Weyes Blood</div>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">Cinematic, baroque pop with an old-soul feel.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="polaroid">
            <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hairooo/index/refs/heads/main/images/MattMaltese.jpg" alt="Matt Maltese">
            <div class="polaroid-caption">Matt Maltese</div>
            <div class="polaroid-detail">Ballroom pop filled with dry wit and romance.</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <article class="paper-scrap about-scrap">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive; color: var(--accent-green);">About Me</h3>
        [span_4](start_span)<p>Hello! I'm Gabriel[span_4](end_span).</p>
        [span_5](start_span)<p>A **20-year-old** second-year **Nursing student** at **Bicol University Tabaco**[span_5](end_span).</p>
        [span_6](start_span)<p><strong>Hobbies:</strong> Listening to music, binge-watching, and sleeping[span_6](end_span).</p>
        <hr>
        <p style="font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9rem;">
            "Love isn't something that weak people do. Being a romantic takes a hell of a lot of hope." <br>
            <span style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">— Fleabag</span>
        </p>
    </article>

    <article class="paper-scrap songs-scrap">
        <div class="tape"></div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Homemade Apple', cursive;">Currently on Repeat</h3>
        
        <div class="song-item">
            [span_7](start_span)<strong>Harbor</strong> — Clairo[span_7](end_span)
            <iframe width="100%" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6m6S_6B2Iaw" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="song-item">
            [span_8](start_span)<strong>Rilkean Heart</strong> — Cocteau Twins[span_8](end_span)
            <iframe width="100%" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/7V-M7qBvG8A" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="song-item">
            [span_9](start_span)<strong>Andromeda</strong> — Weyes Blood[span_9](end_span)
            <iframe width="100%" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Rgp_9j-N55E" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="song-item">
            [span_10](start_span)<strong>Dreams</strong> — Fleetwood Mac[span_10](end_span)
            <iframe width="100%" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Y3ywicffOj4" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
        </div>

        <div class="song-item">
            [span_11](start_span)<strong>As the Irony Would Have It</strong> — Matt Maltese[span_11](end_span)
            <iframe width="100%" height="113" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fA369qZp7sU" frameborder="0" allow="encrypted-media"></iframe>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>

</body>
</html>
